This is a spot on review by one of our guests: "This is a no-frill hostel type situation. You get exactly what’s described and what you paid for. You get a small private room in a large apartment-like layout. The bed is very comfortable and fits two easily. There’s a night stand and a lamp, as well as a rack to hang up your clothes and a mirror on the wall. All the above takes up the entire room. There is hardly any more space. When you check in, the linens are changed and you get fresh towels. They can do with a new set of each to be honest. There are two shared bathrooms, one for men and another for women. It was mostly kept clean for the entire week we stayed there. There’s a kitchen with a table and stove where you can cook some basic meals. There’s a free washer/dryer which were a perfect addition. There are about 8 rooms all in all. The walls are paper thin and it can be a little noisy, and there’s a lingering odor in the place from being old. The location is the best you’ll find
The space is a cozy home away home , from  the decor to the ambiance, I did this with love , love you will feel from the time you come in.

column2: Kalani Hawaii is not your typical "place to stay." As a fusion of all accommodation styles, we are a unique, boutique Private Lodging offering our guests the finest accommodations on the North Shore. Our rooms are rented out individually or joined in privacy for families or groups of travelers. What you will experience at Kalani Hawaii is an escape from the everyday rush, a peek through the palm trees to see how life exists when you're on island time. We offer once in a lifetime memory, beautiful vistas, breathtaking sunsets, and short strolls to famous beaches, snorkeling, world class surfing, and much, much more. Your personal day begins when you want it to and only requires you to share the sand and warm Pacific with sleepy turtles, tropical fish, jumping porpoise - and surfers during our winter big wave season. Oh yes, and you'll find many others just like you, in awe of our sunsets that truly have no rival on either side of the equator, so enjoy every second of your stay!

El baño presenta una ducha a nivel del suelo con divisoria de vidrio templado y dispone de cómodos sanitarios, además de espejo y dos cajoneras. Todas las ventanas disponen de doble cortina para oscurecer el ambiente o dejar que pase la luz natura

We founded this house neglected, run down and decrepit but saw beauty within its colonial Architraves, Kauri Pine and Red cedar stair case, Sandstone window sills and natural Victorian Charm which led us to our restoration to its former colonial glory.
